            "text": "Reverse charge applies to goods transport agency services, not to the goods themselves. Where a GTA has not opted for forward charge, specified recipients such as companies, factories, registered partnerships and any GST registered person pay 5% GST directly to the government and can claim it as input tax credit. Unregistered individual truck owners are exempt."
